text: Mikhail Petrovich Nenashev (18 March 1960 - 29 August 2021) was a Russian politician. He was born in the Ternovsky District, Russia. Nenashev was a member of the Party of Business. Between 2007 until 2011, Nenashev was a member of the State Duma. Nenashev died on 29 August 2021 from cardiac arrest in Moscow, aged 61.В одном из московских фитнес-клубов скончался бывший депутат Госдумы Михаил Ненашев ==References== Category:1960 births Category:2021 deaths Category:Members of the State Duma Category:Deaths from cardiac arrest Category:People from Voronezh Oblast
